    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      286.6,
      495.7,
      299.88
    ],
    "text": "In light of these materials, I do not see any reason to issue the interim order prayed for.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      321.28,
      526.28,
      334.56
    ],
    "text": "In the context of child custody in Sri Lanka, habeas corpus can be used to resolve custody",
