      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      341.92,
      526.42,
      355.2
    ],
    "text": "disputes when one party alleges that a child is being wrongfully detained by the other party,",
