      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      418.0,
      526.37,
      431.28
    ],
    "text": "There are no materials to substantiate to suggest that the corpus is in illegal custody as in this",
