      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      148.33,
      412.63,
      161.61
    ],
    "text": "Therefore, I do not see any reason to issue the writ of habeas corpus.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      183.01,
      526.37,
      196.29
    ],
    "text": "In the case of Rajeswari Chandrasekar Ganesh Vs. The State of Tamil Nadu - Writ Petition",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      203.77,
      335.71,
      217.05
    ],
    "text": "(Criminal) No. 402 of 2021 J.B.Pardiwala J. held that;",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      238.45,
      526.04,
      251.73
    ],
    "text": "The writ of Habeas Corpus is a prerogative writ and an extraordinary remedy. It is",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      259.09,
      526.04,
      272.37
    ],
    "text": "a writ of right and not a writ of course and may be granted only on reasonable ground or",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      279.88,
      526.27,
      293.16
    ],
    "text": "probable cause being shown, as held by this Court in Mohd. Ikram Hussain v. State of Uttar",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      300.52,
      526.4,
      313.8
    ],
    "text": "Pradesh and others, AIR 1964 SC 1625 and Kanu Sanyal v. District Magistrate, Darjeeling,",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      321.28,
      171.74,
      334.56
    ],
    "text": "(1973) 2 SCC 674.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      355.96,
      526.06,
      369.24
    ],
    "text": "However, parents must exercise caution and refrain from exposing their children to personal",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      376.6,
      526.09,
      389.88
    ],
    "text": "problems. Just as it is our duty to shield them from physical harm, so too must we protect",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      397.36,
      526.14,
      410.64
    ],
    "text": "their emotional well-being. Embarrassing children with adult issues can disrupt their",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      418.0,
      526.34,
      431.28
    ],
    "text": "development and create undue stress. It is incumbent upon parents to provide a stable and",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      438.76,
      526.42,
      452.04
    ],
    "text": "supportive environment, allowing them to thrive without the burden of personal difficulties.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      459.4,
      526.25,
      472.68
    ],
    "text": "In family law, there exists a well-established principle that children should not endure",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      480.18,
      526.38,
      493.46
    ],
    "text": "suffering due to conflicts or issues between their parents. This principle is firmly grounded in",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      500.82,
      526.01,
      514.1
    ],
    "text": "the doctrine of the best interests of the child, which serves as the paramount consideration in",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      521.58,
      229.97,
      534.86
    ],
    "text": "all matters concerning children.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      556.26,
      526.37,
      569.54
    ],
    "text": "In the case of Rajeswari Chandrasekar Ganesh Vs. The State of Tamil Nadu - Writ Petition",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      577.02,
      338.83,
      590.3
    ],
    "text": "(Criminal) No. 402 of 2021 J.B. Pardiwala J. held that;",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      611.7,
      526.04,
      624.98
    ],
    "text": "Before we close this matter, we would like to convey to the parties that their two",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      632.34,
      526.09,
      645.62
    ],
    "text": "minor children are watching them very closely. Showing the children that their parents can",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      653.13,
      526.4,
      666.41
    ],
    "text": "respect each other and resolve the conflict respectfully will give them a good foundation for",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      673.77,
      526.07,
      687.05
    ],
    "text": "the conflict that may, God forbid, arise in their own lives. The parties should try to do their",
