    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      715.17,
      526.25,
      728.45
    ],
    "text": "problems and children. It is of utmost interest to protect the innocence of children and allow",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      735.92,
      526.2,
      749.21
    ],
    "text": "them to remain children. They must not be burdened by any adult problem. Minor children do",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      781.18,
      525.92,
      805.66
    ],
    "text": "Page 6 of 6",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      72.23,
      525.97,
      85.51
    ],
    "text": "not have the coping skills or the intellectual ability to understand any issues like the financial",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      92.89,
      402.79,
      106.17
    ],
    "text": "constraints, adult relationship issues or their parents unhappiness.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      127.69,
      526.25,
      140.97
    ],
    "text": "After careful consideration of all materials before us, I find no compelling justification to",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
